The reception will be held at the castle of Vajdahunyad, located in the Bois de ville, and according to the communication from the ministry, 1,000 forints per person are calculated for the hundred guests.
According to the press service, it will be a very simple cocktail to which only foreign diplomats accredited in Hungary will be invited.
