However, a good pop song can be sincere too.
The attitude of reception works in this spirit also independently of language or borders.
hvg.hu: Do you see a difference between Hungarian and foreign audiences, is one or the other more open to your music?
Zs.B.: Abroad, especially in the West, light music has older traditions.
