The song also says that we have to forget our ego a bit, forget who comes from where, who goes where, we just have to let these wings, the wings of love, carry us.
I wanted others to also feel that euphoric state that we felt when the song was born.
hvg.hu: Which of the songs made you work the most?
Zs.B.: To be honest, none about the music creation process, we had some more difficult songs when mixing.
