Our economy has already been going through a phase of growth for several years, just like the rest of the world, and ČSSD does not fail to brag about it.
It was a unique opportunity for the successive governments of this party to regularize public finances.
However, instead of that, they indebted the State more and more.
Other countries, apart from a few exceptions like Hungary, Albania or Egypt, have managed their affairs in a much more reasonable way than our republic.
It is a monstrous disgrace that essentially falls on previous governments.
We are one of the countries which, on a global scale, are the least threatened by poverty.
