The Congress approves the transposition of the Mifid, which entered into force on November 1
Parallel to its parliamentary formality, which ended today with the vote of the Congress of the amendments incorporated into the project in the Senate, the Government submitted to a public hearing the regulations that will develop the new law, with the aim of its entry into force before the year ends.
The representatives of the various groups agreed to highlight the effort made by the deputies and senators to negotiate and agree on the best regulations capable of guaranteeing the protection of investors and regulating in detail the activity of the organizations so that the markets operate efficiently.
The Mifid, which modifies the Securities Market Law, involves the modernization of financial markets, while strengthening investor protection, improving the powers of the leaders of the National Securities Market Commission (CNMV) and promoting the cooperation between the different leaders of the European Union.
The new regulations will make it possible to provide financial advisory services both to specialized companies and to natural or legal persons and creates a new type of financial services (ESIS), financial advisory companies (AFI), which merge with companies companies, securities agencies and portfolio management companies.
In addition, it increases the number of systems for the execution of operations on financial instruments, so that it is possible to add to the regulated secondary markets multilateral trading systems and order internationalization systems, which face competition to the current stock market managers.
The Law also obliges investment services companies to disclose to the market information on key aspects of its business profile, risk exposure and forms of risk management and obliges them to keep a register of all the operations they carry out, to facilitate control by the CNMV.
Going through the Congressional Economics Committee, several changes were added, including one that highlights that secured debt will be considered a &quot;complex&quot; financial instrument given its high risk for the investor, who demonstrated with what happened with US high-risk (subprime) mortgage debt.
In addition, they took advantage of the transposition of the direction took advantage to legally delimit the functions that the graduates in Economics can have 30 years after that in 1977, was approved, the royal decree that delimits the professional functions reserved to the economists.
For its part, the Senate has incorporated the creation of new figures in the financial sector, such as that of the mediator, who will work on behalf of a company, who will not require the authorization of the CNMV and who will be able to provide marketing products and attracting new clients to different investment firms at the same time.
The harmonized consumer price index increases by five tenths in November, up to 4.1%
This indicator, which is then used by Eurostat to incorporate it into the calculation of the inflation rate in the European Union, provides an assessment of the evolution of prices in Spain during the month of November.
Its publication responds to the policy of Eurostat and the European Central Bank (ECB) by offering data comparable in time and quality to those produced in the United States.
The leading indicator is calculated using the same process as that used for the Harmonized Consumer Price Index, but using various statistical modeling methods to estimate information that is not yet available at the time of publication. .
INE recalled that the information provided by the leading indicator is only indicative, because it does not necessarily have to coincide with the definitive data which will be revealed on December 14th.
&quot;The CPI will continue at relatively high levels&quot;
